Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.81,0:00:08.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.25,0:00:14.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kourin...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.25,0:00:16.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.46,0:00:19.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Good morning, Kourin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.36,0:00:21.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you stop being so formal with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.65,0:00:23.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.94,0:00:25.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... right...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.77,0:00:28.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That Sendou guy is so lucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:31.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try talking to Kourin, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:34.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Sup?! You two are here early!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.81,0:00:36.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Naoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.69,0:00:37.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.02,0:00:39.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack... Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.94,0:00:42.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How did he get so chummy with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.16,0:00:45.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Let me borrow your eraser.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.16,0:00:46.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sendou aside, with Ishida around...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.45,0:00:46.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.05,0:00:49.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kourin's getting farther and farther away!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:56.03,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Vanguard Monthly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.93,0:00:55.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna talk to you, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:33.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi, I changed my first Vanguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.16,0:02:36.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I tried puttin' in \Nall kinds of cards, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.82,0:02:39.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that, by trying all \Nkinds of things like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:42.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll eventually hit on the deck \Nthat's perfect for you. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.94,0:02:43.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:46.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. That's what I figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.82,0:02:48.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I a natural or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:50.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sendou, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.08,0:02:56.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach us about Vanguard... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:04.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Specifically, the secret attacks \Nwe need to beat Kourin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:06.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Secret attacks...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:07.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.74,0:03:12.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, like this, you ride and then attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:16.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you put in more critical triggers,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.85,0:03:20.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll give you an attack-centered \Ndeck that easily delivers damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:28.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! Now we'll be able to \Nenjoy club life with Kourin, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:34.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.89,0:03:37.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our club life with Kourin...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:40.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She wiped the floor with them again...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.73,0:03:44.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they are just learning how to play...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:49.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit teaching all of these people!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:52.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Vanguard, so I just couldn't refuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:53.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:58.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't come to this school so I could \Nbe in a club with guys hitting on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:04.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, why did you \Ntransfer to this school, Kourin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:06.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And using "Tatsunagi" as your last name...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:09.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:11.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Takuto's idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.74,0:04:14.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's doing a lot to help me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:19.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With the Circuit over, he \Nrecommended going to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:20.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.77,0:04:25.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right there...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:30.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:33.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt like someone was \Nstaring at me just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:38.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody else is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.65,0:04:41.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're an idol, \Nit's probably a stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:43.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even bring up the idea of a stalker!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:46.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you got a weirdo givin' \Nyou trouble, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:48.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take him outta commission!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:49.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Violence isn't the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:51.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd just give him a little beat-down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:53.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}That's still no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:56.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yeah, fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:58.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}But seriously, tell me if \Nthere is that kinda guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:59.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who does that Ishida think he is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:05.70,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Targeted Idol
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:07.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:12.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That idol girl one year below \Nus joined some Cardfight club.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cardfight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:17.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Vanguard?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:21.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a really strong player \Nin the same class as Kourin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:22.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:25.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:29.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh. So Misaki knows him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:33.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But rumor has it that the boy formed \Nthe club to get close to Kourin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:38.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the rumor true?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.18,0:05:42.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's low! Making a club so \Nhe can get cozy with an idol...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:44.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His ulterior motive is so obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.13,0:05:50.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi and Kourin...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:57.62,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Cardfight Club\N Members Wanted\NBeginners welcome!! I'll teach you the rules!\N1-A Aichi Sendou
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.53,0:06:02.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We need two more members to \Nofficially establish the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:05.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who says it has to be an official club?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:09.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kourin, you said you wanted it to be a club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:12.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.82,0:06:16.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it'll be okay. I'm sure \Nwe'll find more people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.09,0:06:19.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki! Perfect timing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:21.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run in the hallway!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:23.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:26.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki, I've started a Cardfight Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:28.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With Kourin...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:30.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So I hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:33.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you join too, Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:36.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, the people at Hitsue High \Nstarted a Vanguard Club, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:40.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, we may be able to have \Nan intramural high school tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:42.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be in a tournament together again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.06,0:06:47.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I can't join. \NI've got the shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:50.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:54.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure you could find a little \Ntime to participate in the club...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:56.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Aichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:07:01.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They call this girl the \N"Boss Lady of Miyaji Academy"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:03.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.58,0:07:06.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you for your own \Ngood. Steer clear of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:08.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:12.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry, Misaki. I'll see you later...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.61,0:07:23.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! I lost again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:24.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:26.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.53,0:07:29.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! This shouldn't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:30.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:32.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:35.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You turned him down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:37.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to work here at the shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.05,0:07:40.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, you've \Ngot this guy to help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:45.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, though I'd only be an \Nassistant to the sub-manager. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:49.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? \NThis is my family's shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.66,0:07:52.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm able to work, it only \Nmakes sense that I work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:58.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, true, but since you go to the same \Nschool as Aichi, you oughta be in the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:07:59.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:01.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already made up my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:05.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it looks like Aichi's \Nalready got new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:08.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, what a waste...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:11.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Miwa! Izaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:14.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get over here and fight the great Katsumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:17.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:19.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on our way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.28,0:08:26.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, if I want to play \NVanguard, I can do it right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:29.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is that a new deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:33.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've finally made a \Nnew deck for yourself, Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:36.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're racing through the blossom of \Nyouth with Vanguard beside you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:38.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I envy you! I sure do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:40.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:45.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:49.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:55.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida isn't here today. Now's my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:09:00.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy? I think his name is Shingo Komoi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:03.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:05.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:07.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:12.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stalking Kourin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:13.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:15.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This magazine is proof plenty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.41,0:09:16.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:19.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! It'll be easier \Non you if you confess!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:21.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this, a cop show?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:21.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it ain't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:22.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:25.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is Kourin's stalker!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:27.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, admit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:29.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:32.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?! This guy doesn't \Nknow when to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.12,0:09:34.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How 'bout I pop you one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:37.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No fighting, Naoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:39.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:41.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:44.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A fight would be wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:44.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:48.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight me with this, Naoki Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.20,0:09:50.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?! He's got...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:53.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Vanguard deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.08,0:09:55.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll fight to the finish...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:59.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...and then I'll make you promise to stay away \Nfrom the person who means a lot to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:03.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bring it on! I'll give you a crack at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:13.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up, Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:16.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ambush Dragon Eradicator, Linchu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:21.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stealth Dragon, Magatsu Wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.28,0:10:30.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I go first! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.74,0:10:33.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ride Stealth Beast, Night Panther!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:35.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:37.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magatsu Wind moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:40.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's your turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:41.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Naoki Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:59.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ride Demolition Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:01.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Linchu moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.92,0:11:03.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I call Dui!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.09,0:11:09.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk... What's he snickerin' about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:12.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go! Demolition Dragon \Nattacks Night Panther!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:15.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Drive trigger check!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:18.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I got a trigger right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.48,0:11:22.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I give +5000 power to Dui. And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.48,0:11:27.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.61,0:11:30.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an absolute beginner, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:35.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind the stand trigger, but \Nyou attack first with your Vanguard?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:37.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:43.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk... Makin' fun of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:47.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Linchu boosts! Dui attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:53.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! 2 damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.64,0:11:59.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You get excited about {\i1}that{\i0}? \NYou really are a beginner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:02.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd get crabby if I steamrolled you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:06.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll do you a favor just this once \Nand teach you some basic tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.57,0:12:09.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Clam it about that beginner stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:13.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being polite! After all, I'm \Nsaying "beginner," not "noob."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:17.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:20.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ride Magatsu Gale!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:22.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I call!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.94,0:12:24.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.73,0:12:28.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you attack, it's a given that \Nyou start with a rear-guard unit,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.61,0:12:32.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then attack with your Vanguard, and \Nthen with your other rear-guard unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:38.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do that, and your stand trigger \Nwon't go to waste like last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:40.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll also have room to allocate \Ncritical triggers or power-up effects
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.68,0:12:44.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,to your units based on \Nyour opponent's guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:49.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I doubt you're able to comprehend \Nmy explanation with words alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:53.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so you can learn by watching my attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:57.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bloody Mist attacks Demolition Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:00.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:03.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Susei goes to the damage zone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.65,0:13:07.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! My Vanguard, Magatsu Gale, attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:08.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:11.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Drive trigger check!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:14.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd gotten a stand trigger here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:18.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be able to stand up Bloody Mist, \Nwhich has already attacked once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.01,0:13:21.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:30.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, my final rear-guard attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:37.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's one of the fundamentals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:40.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like, you can try \Nit out during your next turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:46.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's givin' me a handicap?! Punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:48.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I stand and draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.08,0:13:54.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ride Thunder Boom Dragon! \NAnd then I call Spark Rain Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.94,0:13:57.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Spark Rain attacks Magatsu Gale!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:14:00.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! That's the way you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:01.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not going through.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:03.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:07.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...! Thunder Boom Dragon attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:14.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Linchu boosts! Dui attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:20.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heal trigger! I heal 1 damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:23.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The damage is 3 to 3?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:25.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! We're tied up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:29.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you thinking that we're evenly matched?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:32.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand and draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.42,0:14:37.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you the difference \Nbetween you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.16,0:14:39.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ride Magatsu Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:48.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When Magatsu Gale is in the Soul, \NMagatsu Storm has 11000 power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:52.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I call Shijimamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:55.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bloody Mist attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:56.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.94,0:15:01.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shijimamaru boosts. Magatsu Storm attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.68,0:15:02.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.20,0:15:04.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Drive check.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.76,0:15:05.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First check.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:06.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:12.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I give the power to White Mane and \Nthe extra critical to Magatsu Storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:19.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! 5 damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:20.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's end it with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:25.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,White Mane attacks with a \Nboost from Magatsu Wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.85,0:15:28.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:30.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.34,0:15:34.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:36.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I got you to 5 damage. Just a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:39.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more, my foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:41.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna torpedo you this turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:45.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the same person I was yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:46.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:50.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike, my avatar! I ride...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:53.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Eradicator, Gauntlet Buster Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.50,0:15:57.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I call Dui and Red River!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:16:00.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Gauntlet Buster Dragon's skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:02.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Especial Counterblast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:05.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I retire one of your rear-guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:11.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Break through the limit! Limit Break!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:15.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate its skill one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One more unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:24.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Burn through the ultimate limit! Limit Break!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:30.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a total of 17000 power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:31.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And three criticals!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:34.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go! Show him what a man you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:38.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Linchu boosts! Dui attacks Magatsu Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:41.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bloody Mist intercepts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.08,0:16:43.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:45.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the same person I was yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:49.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dui, lend Gauntlet Buster your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:53.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:16:59.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what's wrong with beginners.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:00.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:03.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.49,0:17:06.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have this card in my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.85,0:17:08.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?! Perfect guard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:14.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dang it! Drive check!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:16.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:18.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I give all of the effects to Spark Rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:20.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm countin' on you, Spark Rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:23.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blow Magatsu Storm away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:29.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:32.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can protect myself this \Nnext turn, I can win this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:36.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:40.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,that if you successfully defend \Nyourself this turn, you can beat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:43.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:46.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Again, this is what's wrong with beginners.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:49.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You stacked your deck with Eradicators,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:53.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,yet the first stand trigger you \Ndrew wasn't an Eradicator card...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:58.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you're confident about \Nwinning with that half-baked deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:00.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoki...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:05.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, Sendou, why did you let a\N beginner like this into the club?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:08.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:12.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't fathom why he's \Nin the Cardfight Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:15.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?! What have \Nyou got against me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:19.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you asked, I'll explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:22.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was this spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.28,0:18:28.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though there's nothing more \Nwonderful in the world than Vanguard,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:31.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone at this academy is so devoted to \Ntheir studies that they pay it no attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:33.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but this is where I met my hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:38.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about the greatest of the great, \Nthe backbone of the Vanguard world in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:43.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd only seen my hero on TV, but now, \Nin front of me, in the flesh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:46.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, a miracle occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:50.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My hero formed a Cardfight \NClub at this academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:56.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Every day, I waited for my chance \Nto strike up a conversation...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.98,0:19:01.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But standing next to my idol every single \Nmoment is this juvenile delinquent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:09.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! You've destroyed every \Nchance I got by being a hanger-on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:11.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have I been with Kourin that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:14.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When did I say anything about Kourin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:15.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Not her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:16.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:18.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Aichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:22.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Sendou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.84,0:19:26.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy doesn't have the faintest \Nidea of how great you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:29.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you playing Vanguard \Nwith somebody like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:30.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:35.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:38.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...is being poisoned by \Na juvenile delinquent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:37.36,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Champion of the VF Circuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:38.61,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Team Q4 Won!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:41.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot accept that reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:39.61,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi Sendou Achieved Great Results!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.37,0:19:46.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I'll win this fight and free Sendou!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:50.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Magatsu Storm's skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:52.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Limit Break!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.97,0:20:02.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Magatsu-style Ninjutsu, \NSecret Demon Dragon Avatar skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.17,0:20:06.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I call!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.69,0:20:10.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magatsu Breath boosts! Magatsu Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:11.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:15.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shijimamaru boosts! Magatsu Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.72,0:20:16.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.22,0:20:19.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Final judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.77,0:20:23.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magatsu Storm attacks with \Na boost from Night Panther!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:31.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, draw the top card from your deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:33.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A damage check that will decide destiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:39.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:40.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:45.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally. So, set Sendou free.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:49.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?! Is there something you want to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:50.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:51.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:53.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Komoi, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:55.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:57.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Join the Cardfight Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.68,0:21:03.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you know so much about Vanguard, \Nteach me more about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.29,0:21:04.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:06.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi! Help me out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.98,0:21:09.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy should be in the club!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.28,0:21:14.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! He can join, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:16.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But all he did was beat Ishida...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.82,0:21:19.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We could both tell that \Nhe's got plenty of skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:23.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, he already passed \Nour membership qualification,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.14,0:21:25.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,beating a member of the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:27.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:29.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, you can join.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:31.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:32.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.49,0:21:35.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, um... Komoi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:38.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes! I'm Shingo Komoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:41.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Cardfight Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.00,0:21:42.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:45.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna count on you from now on, Bowl-cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.00,0:21:47.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How dare you address me like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.28,0:21:49.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You... You boneheaded beginner, Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:51.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you call me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.25,0:21:54.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There'd be no point in me teaching Vanguard
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:57.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,to a muscle-brained dope who's \Nquick to resort to violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.01,0:22:00.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?! How do you figure \NI'm muscle-brained?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.76,0:22:03.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Want another match? This \Ntime, I ain't gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:04.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we just need one more member...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.41,0:22:05.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Oh, now you want another match?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.98,0:22:08.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'd get no thrill from \Nbeating a clueless noob!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.70,0:22:10.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.66,0:22:14.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what's disrupting \Nthe order of the academy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.34,0:22:16.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cardfight Club...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.53,0:22:19.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better report to the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.97,0:23:58.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for welcoming me \Ninto the club, Aichi and Kourin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.68,0:23:59.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.85,0:24:02.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you improve, newbie Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.86,0:24:06.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's a newbie at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.96,0:24:08.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we've got four people.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.06,0:24:10.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One more, and the Cardfight Club \Nis officially established!
